{%- comment -%}
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
ENGRAVED GLASS OPTIONS
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This snippet renders engraved glass options for products where custom.option_set_v2 metafield contains 
"Engraved Glass".

When "Engraving Mandatory" is ALSO present, the glass selection is mandatory (no "No Glass" option).
Otherwise, the glass selection is optional (includes "No Glass" option).

Pint Glass is ONLY available when the product has custom.the_craft_beer_v2 or custom.the_craft_beer metafield set.

Engraved Glass Product: handle "engraved-glass" (ID: 9145343836396)
Options:
  - Glass Type: Rocks Glass, Shot Glass, Pint Glass (conditional)
  - Engraving: Clear Engraving ($30), Gold Color Fill Engraving ($35), Silver Color Fill Engraving ($35)

Variants (9 total - Glass Type / Engraving):
  - Rocks Glass / Clear Engraving: 47255846748396 ($30)
  - Rocks Glass / Gold Color Fill Engraving: 47255846781164 ($35)
  - Rocks Glass / Silver Color Fill Engraving: 47255846813932 ($35)
  - Shot Glass / Clear Engraving: 47255846846700 ($30)
  - Shot Glass / Gold Color Fill Engraving: 47255846879468 ($35)
  - Shot Glass / Silver Color Fill Engraving: 47255846912236 ($35)
  - Pint Glass / Clear Engraving: 47267135979756 ($30)
  - Pint Glass / Gold Color Fill Engraving: (TBD)
  - Pint Glass / Silver Color Fill Engraving: (TBD)

********************************************
Supported variables
********************************************

* product: the product to check for option_set_v2 metafield
* product_form_id: the ID of the main product form (passed to centralized handler)
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- assign engraved_glass_product = all_products['engraved-glass'] -%}

{%- liquid
  assign show_engraved_glass = false
  assign show_pint_glass = false
  assign option_set_metafield = product.metafields.custom.option_set_v2
  if option_set_metafield != blank
    assign option_set_string = option_set_metafield | metafield_text
    if option_set_string contains 'Engraved Glass'
      assign show_engraved_glass = true
    endif
  endif

  comment
    Show Pint Glass option only when the product has the craft beer metafield set
  endcomment
  if product.metafields.custom.the_craft_beer_v2 != blank or product.metafields.custom.the_craft_beer != blank
    assign show_pint_glass = true
  endif
-%}

{%- if show_engraved_glass and engraved_glass_product != blank -%}
  {%- comment -%}Extract unique glass types and engraving types from product options{%- endcomment -%}
  {%- assign all_glass_types = engraved_glass_product.options_by_name['Glass Type'].values -%}
  {%- assign engraving_types = engraved_glass_product.options_by_name['Engraving'].values -%}
  
  {%- comment -%}Filter glass types - only show Pint Glass when craft beer metafield is present{%- endcomment -%}
  {%- assign glass_types = '' -%}
  {%- for glass_type in all_glass_types -%}
    {%- if glass_type == 'Pint Glass' -%}
      {%- if show_pint_glass -%}
        {%- if glass_types == '' -%}
          {%- assign glass_types = glass_type -%}
        {%- else -%}
          {%- assign glass_types = glass_types | append: '|||' | append: glass_type -%}
        {%- endif -%}
      {%- endif -%}
    {%- else -%}
      {%- if glass_types == '' -%}
        {%- assign glass_types = glass_type -%}
      {%- else -%}
        {%- assign glass_types = glass_types | append: '|||' | append: glass_type -%}
      {%- endif -%}
    {%- endif -%}
  {%- endfor -%}
  {%- assign glass_types = glass_types | split: '|||' -%}

  <div class="product-engraved-glass" data-engraved-glass-wrapper data-product-title="{{ product.title | escape }}" data-mandatory="false">
    {%- comment -%}Glass Type Selection{%- endcomment -%}
    <div class="product-engraved-glass__option">

      <div class="product-engraved-glass__radio-group">
        {%- comment -%}
          BB Required Field Validation 2026-05-07 — defensive fix.

          "No Glass" is now always rendered, regardless of the
          `is_mandatory` metafield value. The previous logic conflated two
          different concerns: bottle engraving (which can legitimately be
          mandatory on personalized-only products) and engraved glass
          (which is always an optional upsell). When both flags were set
          via "Engraving Mandatory" in the metafield, customers buying
          standard bottles in /collections/engravings could not opt out of
          paying for an engraved glass.

          We pair this code change with a Matrixify import that removes
          "Engraving Mandatory" from the 90 affected bottle products, but
          this defensive code ensures the bug cannot recur even if that
          metafield value drifts back in via a future product upload.

          The data-mandatory data attribute is hard-coded to "false" so
          downstream JS reads the corrected state (no consumer of that
          attribute outside this snippet).
        {%- endcomment -%}
        <label class="product-engraved-glass__radio-item">
          <input
            type="radio"
            name="engraved_glass_type"
            value="none"
            data-engraved-glass-type-radio
            checked
          >
          <span class="product-engraved-glass__radio-label">No Glass</span>
        </label>

        {%- comment -%}Glass Type Options{%- endcomment -%}
        {%- for glass_type in glass_types -%}
          <label class="product-engraved-glass__radio-item">
            <input
              type="radio"
              name="engraved_glass_type"
              value="{{ glass_type | escape }}"
              data-engraved-glass-type-radio
              data-glass-type="{{ glass_type | escape }}"
            >
            <span class="product-engraved-glass__radio-label">{{ glass_type }}</span>
          </label>
        {%- endfor -%}
      </div>
    </div>

    {%- comment -%}
      Engraving Type Selection — hidden by default since "No Glass" is the
      default selection. JS toggles visibility when a glass is picked.
      Previously controlled by `unless is_mandatory` which is no longer
      a meaningful signal here (BB Required Field Validation 2026-05-07).
    {%- endcomment -%}
    <div class="product-engraved-glass__option product-engraved-glass__engraving-options" data-engraved-glass-engraving-wrapper style="display: none;">
      <label class="product-engraved-glass__label">
        Engraving Type <span class="product-engraved-glass__required">*</span>
      </label>
      
      <div class="product-engraved-glass__radio-group">
        {%- comment -%}Get unique engraving types with their prices{%- endcomment -%}
        {%- for engraving_type in engraving_types -%}
          {%- comment -%}Find a variant with this engraving type to get its price{%- endcomment -%}
          {%- for variant in engraved_glass_product.variants -%}
            {%- if variant.option2 == engraving_type -%}
              {%- assign engraving_price = variant.price -%}
              {%- break -%}
            {%- endif -%}
          {%- endfor -%}
          <label class="product-engraved-glass__radio-item">
            <input 
              type="radio" 
              name="engraved_glass_engraving" 
              value="{{ engraving_type | escape }}"
              data-engraved-glass-engraving-radio
              data-engraving-type="{{ engraving_type | escape }}"
              data-price="{{ engraving_price }}"
              {% if forloop.first %}checked{% endif %}
            >
            <span class="product-engraved-glass__radio-label">
              {{ engraving_type }}
              <span class="product-engraved-glass__price">({{ engraving_price | money }})</span>
            </span>
          </label>
        {%- endfor -%}
      </div>
    </div>

    {%- comment -%}Engraved Glass Text Input - Shown when glass is selected{%- endcomment -%}
    <div class="product-engraved-glass__text-wrapper" data-engraved-glass-text-wrapper style="display: none;">
      <label class="product-engraved-glass__label" for="engraved-glass-text-{{ product.id }}">
        Engraved Glass Text <span class="product-engraved-glass__required">*</span>
      </label>
      <input
        type="text"
        id="engraved-glass-text-{{ product.id }}"
        class="product-engraved-glass__input"
        name="engraved_glass_text"
        data-engraved-glass-text
        placeholder="Initials or Short Messages | Email for Images or Logos"
        maxlength="50"
      >
      <p class="product-engraved-glass__hint">Maximum 50 characters</p>
    </div>

    {%- comment -%}Hidden fields to store glass data{%- endcomment -%}
    <input type="hidden" data-engraved-glass-variant-id value="">
    <input type="hidden" data-engraved-glass-product-title value="{{ product.title | escape }}">
  </div>

  <script>
    (function() {
      'use strict';
      
      // Variant data for lookup
      const variants = [
        {%- for variant in engraved_glass_product.variants -%}
          { id: {{ variant.id }}, option1: "{{ variant.option1 | escape }}", option2: "{{ variant.option2 | escape }}", price: {{ variant.price }} }{% unless forloop.last %},{% endunless %}
        {%- endfor -%}
      ];
      
      function initEngravedGlass() {
        const wrapper = document.querySelector('[data-engraved-glass-wrapper]');
        if (!wrapper) return;
        
        const glassTypeRadios = wrapper.querySelectorAll('[data-engraved-glass-type-radio]');
        const engravingRadios = wrapper.querySelectorAll('[data-engraved-glass-engraving-radio]');
        const engravingWrapper = wrapper.querySelector('[data-engraved-glass-engraving-wrapper]');
        const textWrapper = wrapper.querySelector('[data-engraved-glass-text-wrapper]');
        const textInput = wrapper.querySelector('[data-engraved-glass-text]');
        const variantIdInput = wrapper.querySelector('[data-engraved-glass-variant-id]');
        const productTitle = wrapper.dataset.productTitle;
        const isMandatory = wrapper.dataset.mandatory === 'true';
        
        // Find variant by glass type and engraving type
        function findVariant(glassType, engravingType) {
          return variants.find(v => v.option1 === glassType && v.option2 === engravingType);
        }
        
        // Update the selected variant ID
        function updateSelectedVariant() {
          const selectedGlassRadio = wrapper.querySelector('[data-engraved-glass-type-radio]:checked');
          const selectedEngravingRadio = wrapper.querySelector('[data-engraved-glass-engraving-radio]:checked');
          
          if (!selectedGlassRadio || selectedGlassRadio.value === 'none') {
            variantIdInput.value = '';
            return;
          }
          
          const glassType = selectedGlassRadio.dataset.glassType;
          const engravingType = selectedEngravingRadio?.dataset.engravingType;
          
          if (glassType && engravingType) {
            const variant = findVariant(glassType, engravingType);
            variantIdInput.value = variant ? variant.id : '';
          }
        }
        
        // Handle glass type radio button changes
        glassTypeRadios.forEach(radio => {
          radio.addEventListener('change', function() {
            const selectedValue = this.value;
            
            if (selectedValue === 'none') {
              engravingWrapper.style.display = 'none';
              textWrapper.style.display = 'none';
              textInput.removeAttribute('required');
              textInput.value = '';
              variantIdInput.value = '';
            } else {
              engravingWrapper.style.display = 'block';
              textWrapper.style.display = 'block';
              textInput.setAttribute('required', 'required');
              updateSelectedVariant();
            }
          });
        });
        
        // Handle engraving type radio button changes
        engravingRadios.forEach(radio => {
          radio.addEventListener('change', function() {
            updateSelectedVariant();
          });
        });
        
        // Remove error class on input
        if (textInput) {
          textInput.addEventListener('input', function() {
            this.classList.remove('product-engraved-glass__input--error');
          });
        }
        
        // Initialize variant ID if mandatory (first glass type + first engraving type)
        if (isMandatory) {
          updateSelectedVariant();
        }
        
        // Register engraved glass addon with the centralized handler
        window.productAddons = window.productAddons || {};
        window.productAddons.engravedGlass = {
          getItem: function() {
            const selectedGlassRadio = wrapper.querySelector('[data-engraved-glass-type-radio]:checked');
            const glassVariantId = variantIdInput.value;
            
            if (!glassVariantId || selectedGlassRadio?.value === 'none') {
              return null;
            }
            
            const glassText = textInput.value.trim();
            const selectedEngravingRadio = wrapper.querySelector('[data-engraved-glass-engraving-radio]:checked');
            const glassType = selectedGlassRadio?.dataset.glassType || '';
            const engravingType = selectedEngravingRadio?.dataset.engravingType || '';
            
            return {
              id: parseInt(glassVariantId, 10),
              properties: {
                'For': productTitle,
                'Glass Type': glassType,
                'Engraving Type': engravingType,
                'Engraving Text': glassText
              }
            };
          },
          validate: function() {
            const selectedGlassRadio = wrapper.querySelector('[data-engraved-glass-type-radio]:checked');
            const glassVariantId = variantIdInput.value;
            
            // If mandatory and nothing selected, invalid
            if (isMandatory && (!glassVariantId || selectedGlassRadio?.value === 'none')) {
              return false;
            }
            
            // If not mandatory and nothing selected, valid
            if (!glassVariantId || selectedGlassRadio?.value === 'none') {
              return true;
            }
            
            // Glass selected - text is required
            const glassText = textInput.value.trim();
            if (!glassText) {
              textInput.focus();
              textInput.classList.add('product-engraved-glass__input--error');
              return false;
            }
            return true;
          }
        };
      }
      
      if (document.readyState === 'loading') {
        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', initEngravedGlass);
      } else {
        initEngravedGlass();
      }
    })();
  </script>

  <style>
    .product-engraved-glass {
      margin-bottom: var(--spacing-4, 16px);
    }
    
    .product-engraved-glass__option {
      margin-bottom: var(--spacing-4, 16px);
    }
    
    .product-engraved-glass__engraving-options {
      border-left: 2px solid rgb(var(--border-color, 229, 231, 235));
    }
    
    .product-engraved-glass__label {
      display: block;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2, 8px);
      font-size: var(--text-sm, 14px);
    }
    
    .product-engraved-glass__required {
      color: rgb(var(--error-text, 220, 38, 38));
    }
    
    .product-engraved-glass__radio-group {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: var(--spacing-3, 12px);
    }
    
    .product-engraved-glass__radio-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: var(--spacing-2, 8px);
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: var(--text-sm, 14px);
    }
    
    .product-engraved-glass__radio-item input[type="radio"] {
      width: 18px;
      height: 18px;
      margin: 0;
      cursor: pointer;
      accent-color: rgb(var(--text-primary, 0, 0, 0));
    }
    
    .product-engraved-glass__radio-label {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 4px;
    }
    
    .product-engraved-glass__price {
      color: rgb(var(--text-secondary, 107, 114, 128));
    }
    
    .product-engraved-glass__text-wrapper {
      margin-top: var(--spacing-4, 16px);
    }
    
    .product-engraved-glass__input {
      width: 100%;
      padding: var(--spacing-2-5, 10px) var(--spacing-3, 12px);
      border: 1px solid rgb(var(--border-color, 229, 231, 235));
      border-radius: var(--rounded-xs, 4px);
      font-size: var(--text-base, 16px);
      background: rgb(var(--input-background, 255, 255, 255));
      color: rgb(var(--text-primary, 0, 0, 0));
      transition: border-color 0.2s ease;
    }
    
    .product-engraved-glass__input:focus {
      outline: none;
      border-color: rgb(var(--text-primary, 0, 0, 0));
    }
    
    .product-engraved-glass__input::placeholder {
      color: rgb(var(--text-secondary, 156, 163, 175));
      font-size: var(--text-sm, 14px);
    }
    
    .product-engraved-glass__input--error {
      border-color: rgb(var(--error-text, 220, 38, 38));
    }
    
    .product-engraved-glass__input--error:focus {
      border-color: rgb(var(--error-text, 220, 38, 38));
    }
    
    .product-engraved-glass__hint {
      margin-top: var(--spacing-1, 4px);
      font-size: var(--text-xs, 12px);
      color: rgb(var(--text-secondary, 107, 114, 128));
    }
    
    @media screen and (max-width: 699px) {
      .product-engraved-glass__radio-group {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: var(--spacing-2, 8px);
      }
    }
  </style>
{%- endif -%}
